---
title: Sweet Soy Tofu & Carrot Ribbon Salad with Ponzu Dressing & Coriander
description: You can’t go wrong with tofu. This versatile protein soaks up whatever flavours you add to it, so tonight we’ve tossed it through sweet and savoury Asian spices. The carrot ribbon salad makes the perfect bed to rest it on, adding sweet freshness to this mouthwatering meal.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
